#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:4
msgid "2D Sprite animation"
msgstr "2D精灵动画"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:7
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:9
msgid ""
"In this tutorial, you'll learn how to create 2D animated characters with the "
"AnimatedSprite class and the AnimationPlayer. Typically, when you create or "
"download an animated character, it will come in one of two ways: as "
"individual images or as a single sprite sheet containing all the animation's "
"frames.  Both can be animated in Godot with the AnimatedSprite class."
msgstr ""
"在本教程中，您将学习如何使用 ``AnimatedSprite`` 类和 ``AnimationPlayer`` 创建"
"2D动画化的角色。通常，当您创建或下载一个动画化的角色时，它将以以下两种方式之"
"一出现：作为单个图像、或包含所有动画帧的单张精灵表。两者都可以使用 "
"``AnimatedSprite`` 类在Godot中进行动画处理。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:14
msgid ""
"First, we'll use :ref:`AnimatedSprite <class_AnimatedSprite>` to animate a "
"collection of individual images. Then we will animate a sprite sheet using "
"this class.  Finally, we will learn another way to animate a sprite sheet "
"with :ref:`AnimationPlayer <class_AnimationPlayer>` and the *Animation* "
"property of :ref:`Sprite <class_Sprite>`."
msgstr ""
"首先，我们将使用 :ref:`AnimatedSprite <class_AnimatedSprite>` 来动画化一组单"
"张图像。然后，我们将使用此类为动画化一个精灵表。最后，我们将学习另一种使用 :"
"ref:`AnimationPlayer <class_AnimationPlayer>` 和 :ref:`Sprite "
"<class_Sprite>` 的 *Animation* 属性，动画化一个精灵表的方法。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:19
msgid ""
"Art for the following examples by https://opengameart.org/users/ansimuz and "
"by https://opengameart.org/users/tgfcoder"
msgstr ""
"以下示例的美术作品由 https://opengameart.org/users/ansimuz 和 https://"
"opengameart.org/users/tgfcoder 提供"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:23
msgid "Individual images with AnimatedSprite"
msgstr "单独图像使用 ``AnimatedSprite``"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:25
msgid ""
"In this scenario, you have a collection of images, each containing one of "
"your character's animation frames. For this example, we'll use the following "
"animation:"
msgstr ""
"在这种情况下，您有一个图像集合，每个图像包含角色的动画帧之一。在此示例中，我"
"们将使用以下动画："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:31
msgid ""
"You can download the images here: :download:`run_animation.zip <files/"
"run_animation.zip>`"
msgstr ""
"您可以在此处下载图像：:download:`run_animation.zip <files/run_animation.zip>`"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:34
msgid ""
"Unzip the images and place them in your project folder. Set up your scene "
"tree with the following nodes:"
msgstr "解压缩这些图像并将它们放在项目文件夹中。使用以下节点设置场景树："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:39
#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:143
msgid ""
"The root node could also be :ref:`Area2D <class_Area2D>` or :ref:"
"`RigidBody2D <class_RigidBody2D>`. The animation will still be made in the "
"same way. Once the animation is completed, you can assign a shape to the "
"CollisionShape2D. See :ref:`Physics Introduction <doc_physics_introduction>` "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"根节点也可以是 :ref:`Area2D <class_Area2D>` 或 :ref:`RigidBody2D "
"<class_RigidBody2D>`。动画仍将以相同方式制作。动画完成后，可以将形状分配给 "
"``CollisionShape2D``。有关更多信息，请参阅 :ref:`物理简介 "
"<doc_physics_introduction>`。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:46
msgid ""
"Now select the ``AnimatedSprite`` and in its *SpriteFrames* property, select "
"\"New SpriteFrames\"."
msgstr ""
"现在，选择 ``AnimatedSprite``，并在其 ``SpriteFrames`` 属性中，选择 ``新建"
"SpriteFrame（New SpriteFrames）``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:51
msgid ""
"Click on the new SpriteFrames resource and you'll see a new panel appear at "
"the bottom of the editor window:"
msgstr ""
"点击新的 ``SpriteFrames`` 资源，您将看到一个新面板，出现在编辑器窗口的底部："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:56
msgid ""
"From the FileSystem dock on the left side, drag the 8 individual images into "
"the center part of the SpriteFrames panel. On the left side, change the name "
"of the animation from \"default\" to \"run\"."
msgstr ""
"从左边的文件系统停靠面板，将这8张独立的图片拖放到 ``精灵帧（SpriteFrame）`` "
"面板的中间部分。在左边，将动画名称从 ``默认（default）`` 更改为 ``奔跑（run）"
"``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:62
msgid ""
"Back in the Inspector, check the box for the *Playing* property. You should "
"now see the animation playing in the viewport. However, it is a bit slow. To "
"fix this, change the *Speed (FPS)* setting in the SpriteFrames panel to 10."
msgstr ""
"回到属性检查器，选中 ``播放（Playing）`` 属性的复选框。您现在应该可以看到在视"
"图中播放的动画。然而，它有点慢。为了解决这个问题，更改在 ``精灵帧"
"（SpriteFrame）`` 面板中的 *速度(每秒帧数)（Speed (FPS)）* 设置为10。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:66
msgid ""
"You can add additional animations by clicking the \"New Animation\" button "
"and adding additional images."
msgstr ""
"您可以通过点击 ``新建动画（New Animation）`` 按钮，并添加额外的图像，来添加额"
"外的动画。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:70
msgid "Controlling the animation"
msgstr "控制动画"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:72
msgid ""
"Once the animation is complete, you can control the animation via code using "
"the ``play()`` and ``stop()`` methods. Here is a brief example to play the "
"animation while the right arrow key is held, and stop it when the key is "
"released."
msgstr ""
"一旦动画制作完成后，您可以使用 ``play()`` 和 ``stop()`` 方法通过代码控制动"
"画。这是一个简短的示例，在按住右箭头键的同时播放动画，并在释放键时将其停止。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:90
msgid "Sprite sheet with AnimatedSprite"
msgstr "精灵表使用 ``AnimatedSprite``"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:92
msgid ""
"You can also easily animate from a sprite sheet with the class "
"``AnimatedSprite``.  We will use this public domain sprite sheet:"
msgstr ""
"您还可以使用 ``AnimatedSprite`` 类轻松地从一个精灵表制作动画。我们将使用以下"
"公共领域的精灵表："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:96
msgid ""
"Right-click the image and choose \"Save Image As\" to download it, and then "
"copy the image into your project folder."
msgstr ""
"右键点击图片，选择 ``图片另存为（Save Image As）`` 来下载，然后将图像复制到你"
"的项目文件夹中。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:98
msgid ""
"Set up your scene tree the same way you did previously when using individual "
"images.  Select the ``AnimatedSprite`` and in its *SpriteFrames* property, "
"select \"New SpriteFrames\"."
msgstr ""
"与以前使用单独图像时相同的方式设置场景树。选择 ``AnimatedSprite``，并在其 "
"``SpriteFrames`` 属性中，选择 ``新建SpriteFrame（New SpriteFrames）``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:101
msgid ""
"Click on the new SpriteFrames resource.  This time, when the bottom panel "
"appears, select \"Add frames from a Sprite Sheet\"."
msgstr ""
"单击新建的 ``SpriteFrames`` 资源。这次，当底部面板出现时，选择 ``从精灵表添加"
"帧（Add frames from a Sprite Sheet）``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:105
msgid "You will be prompted to open a file.  Select your sprite sheet."
msgstr "系统将提示您打开文件。选择您的精灵表。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:107
msgid ""
"A new window will open, showing your sprite sheet.  The first thing you will "
"need to do is to change the number of vertical and horizontal images in your "
"sprite sheet.  In this sprite sheet, we have four images horizontally and "
"two images vertically."
msgstr ""
"一个新窗口将打开，显示您的精灵表。您需要做的第一件事是更改精灵表中垂直和水平"
"图像的数量。在此精灵表中，水平有四个图像，垂直有两个图像。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:111
msgid ""
"Next, select the frames from the sprite sheet that you want to include in "
"your animation.  We will select the top four, then click \"Add 4 frames\" to "
"create the animation."
msgstr ""
"接下来，从精灵表中选择要包含在动画中的帧。我们将选择前四个，然后点击 ``添加4"
"帧（Add 4 frames）`` 以创建动画。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:115
msgid ""
"You will now see your animation under the list of animations in the bottom "
"panel.  Double click on default to change the name of the animation to jump."
msgstr ""
"现在，您将在底部面板的动画列表下看到您的动画。双击默认值以更改要跳转的动画的"
"名称。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:119
msgid ""
"Finally, check Playing on the  AnimatedSprite in the inspector to see your "
"frog jump!"
msgstr "最后，在属性检查器中选中 ``在AnimatedSprite上播放`` 以查看您的青蛙跳！"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:125
msgid "Sprite sheet with AnimationPlayer"
msgstr "精灵表用 ``AnimationPlayer``"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:127
msgid ""
"Another way that you can animate when using a sprite sheet is to use a "
"standard :ref:`Sprite <class_Sprite>` node to display the texture, and then "
"animating the change from texture to texture with :ref:`AnimationPlayer "
"<class_AnimationPlayer>`."
msgstr ""
"使用精灵表时，可以动画化的另一种方法是使用一个标准的 :ref:`Sprite "
"<class_Sprite>` 节点来显示纹理，然后使用 :ref:`AnimationPlayer "
"<class_AnimationPlayer>` 动画化纹理到纹理的变化。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:131
msgid "Consider this sprite sheet, which contains 6 frames of animation:"
msgstr "考虑一下这个精灵表，包含动画的6帧："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:135
msgid ""
"Right-click the image and choose \"Save Image As\" to download, then copy "
"the image into your project folder."
msgstr ""
"右键点击图片，选择 ``图片另存为（Save Image As）`` 来下载，然后将图像复制到项"
"目文件夹中。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:138
msgid ""
"Our goal is to display these images one after another in a loop. Start by "
"setting up your scene tree:"
msgstr ""
"我们的目的是，在一个循环中一个接一个地显示这些图像。首先设置你的场景树："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:150
msgid ""
"Drag the spritesheet into the Sprite's *Texture* property, and you'll see "
"the whole sheet displayed on the screen. To slice it up into individual "
"frames, expand the *Animation* section in the Inspector and set the "
"*Hframes* to ``6``. *Hframes* and *Vframes* are the number of horizontal and "
"vertical frames in your sprite sheet."
msgstr ""
"将精灵表拖拽到精灵的 ``纹理（Texture）`` 属性中，你会看到整个表显示在屏幕上。"
"把它分割成单独的帧，在属性检查器中展开 ``动画（Animation）`` 部分，将 ``水平"
"帧（Hframes）`` 设置为 ``6``。``水平帧（Hframes）`` 和 ``垂直帧（Vframes）`` "
"是，精灵表中水平和垂直帧的数量。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:158
msgid ""
"Now try changing the value of the *Frame* property. You'll see that it "
"ranges from ``0`` to ``5`` and the image displayed by the Sprite changes "
"accordingly. This is the property we'll be animating."
msgstr ""
"现在尝试更改 ``帧（Frame）`` 属性的值。您将看到它的范围从 ``0`` 到 ``5``，``"
"精灵（Sprite）`` 所显示的图像也随之改变。这就是我们想要动画化的属性。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:162
msgid ""
"Select the ``AnimationPlayer`` and click the \"Animation\" button followed "
"by \"New\". Name the new animation \"walk\". Set the animation length to "
"``0.6`` and click the \"Loop\" button so that our animation will repeat."
msgstr ""
"选择 ``动画播放器（AnimationPlayer）``，然后点击 ``动画（Animation）`` 按钮，"
"然后点击 ``新建（New）`` 按钮。将新动画命名为 ``走路（walk）``。将动画长度设"
"置为 ``0.6``，点击 ``循环（Loop）`` 按钮，动画将会重复。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:168
msgid ""
"Now select the ``Sprite`` node and click the key icon to add a new track."
msgstr "现在选择 ``精灵（Sprite）`` 节点，并点击钥匙图标，添加一个新的轨道。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:172
msgid ""
"Continue adding frames at each point in the timeline (``0.1`` seconds by "
"default), until you have all the frames from 0 to 5. You'll see the frames "
"actually appearing in the animation track:"
msgstr ""
"继续在时间轴的每一点添加帧（默认为 ``0.1`` 秒），直到你已经添加了从0到5的所有"
"帧。你会看到这些帧实际上出现在动画轨道中："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:178
msgid "Press \"Play\" on the animation to see how it looks."
msgstr "按下动画上的 ``播放（Play）`` 键，看看效果如何。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:183
msgid "Controlling an AnimationPlayer animation"
msgstr "控制一个 ``AnimationPlayer`` 动画"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:185
msgid ""
"Like with AnimatedSprite, you can control the animation via code using the "
"``play()`` and ``stop()`` methods. Again, here is an example to play the "
"animation while the right arrow key is held, and stop it when the key is "
"released."
msgstr ""
"与 ``AnimatedSprite`` 一样，您可以使用 ``play()`` 和 ``stop()`` 方法通过代码"
"控制动画。同样，这里有一个示例，在按住右箭头键的同时播放动画，并在释放键时将"
"其停止。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:202
msgid ""
"If updating both an animation and a separate property at once (for example, "
"a platformer may update the sprite's ``h_flip``/``v_flip`` properties when a "
"character turns while starting a 'turning' animation), it's important to "
"keep in mind that ``play()`` isn't applied instantly. Instead, it's applied "
"the next time the :ref:`AnimationPlayer <class_AnimationPlayer>` is "
"processed. This may end up being on the next frame, causing a 'glitch' "
"frame, where the property change was applied but the animation was not. If "
"this turns out to be a problem, after calling ``play()``, you can call "
"``advance(0)`` to update the animation immediately."
msgstr ""
"如果同时更新动画和单独的属性（例如，当角色在启动 ``转向（turning）`` 动画时转"
"向时，平台游戏可能会更新精灵的 ``h_flip``/``v_flip`` 属性），因此务必保持请注"
"意，``play()`` 不会立即应用。取而代之的是，它在下一次处理 :ref:"
"`AnimationPlayer <class_AnimationPlayer>` 时应用。这可能最终出现在下一帧上，"
"导致出现一个 ``小故障（glitch）`` 帧，在该帧中应用了属性更改，但未应用动画。"
"如果这是一个问题，则在调用 ``play()`` 之后，可以调用 ``advance(0)`` 立即更新"
"动画。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:213
msgid "Summary"
msgstr "总结"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/2d/2d_sprite_animation.rst:215
msgid ""
"These examples illustrate the two classes you can use in Godot for 2D "
"animation. ``AnimationPlayer`` is a bit more complex than "
"``AnimatedSprite``, but it provides additional functionality, since you can "
"also animate other properties like position or scale. The class "
"``AnimationPlayer`` can also be used with an ``AnimatedSprite``.  Experiment "
"to see what works best for your needs."
msgstr ""
"这些示例说明了可以在Godot中用于2D动画的两个类。``AnimationPlayer`` 比 "
"``AnimatedSprite`` 稍微复杂一点，但是它提供了额外功能，因此您还可以动画化位置"
"或缩放等其他属性。类 ``AnimationPlayer`` 也可以与 ``AnimatedSprite`` 一起使"
"用。进行实验，看看哪种方法最适合您的需求。"
